New Features and Important Changes in GammaLib 00-04-08

Author(s) : Juergen Knoedlseder

February ??, 2011


1. Introduction
---------------
This document briefly summarizes module by module the most important changes
made since the last release of GammaLib.


2. Configuration
-----------------
Upgrade the license to GPL v3. Remove LICENSE file (license text is given
in file COPYING).


3. Application module
---------------------
None


4. FITS I/O Interface
---------------------
Add create parameter to GFits::open() and the corresponding constructor. This
makes FITS file creation when opening optional. By default, create is set to
false, hence FITS file creation is no longer automatic. This behaviour is
preferred as it provides better control on the creation of new FITS files
(before, FITS files were accidentally created if the filename was mistyped).
Do also not write empty FITS files anymore.


5. Linear algebra module
------------------------
None


