----------------------
None


10. Sky module
--------------
None


11. Support module
------------------
None


12. XML module
--------------
Correctly detect multi-line comments and check for missing closing tags at
the end of the XML file. Update the print() interface (now returns std::string
instead of piping in stream object).


13. Multi-wavelength interface
------------------------------
None


14. Fermi-LAT interface
----------------------
None


